Package com.seailz.discordjv.model.automod

Record Class AutomodRule

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.seailz.discordjv.model.automod.AutomodRule
Record Components:
id - the id of this rule
guild - the guild which this rule belongs to
name - the rule name
creator - the user which first created this rule
event - the rule event type
trigger - the rule trigger type
triggerMetadata - the rule trigger metadata
actions - list of actions to be executed when the rule is triggered
enabled - whether the rule is enabled
exemptRoles - the roles that should not be affected by the rule (Maximum of 20)
exemptChannels - the channels that should not be affected by the rule (Maximum of 50)
All Implemented Interfaces:
Compilerable
public record AutomodRule(String id, Guild guild, String name, User creator, AutomodRule.EventType event, AutomodRule.TriggerType trigger, AutomodRule.TriggerMetadata triggerMetadata, List<AutomodRule.Action> actions, boolean enabled, List<Role> exemptRoles, List<Channel> exemptChannels) extends Record implements Compilerable
Represents a rule in the automod system
